The {{nihongo|'''Yato-no-kami'''|夜刀の神||"gods of the night-sword"}} are snake [[deity|deities]] appearing in the ''[[Hitachi No Kuni Fudoki]]''. They lived in [[Namegata]] county, in fields near the government office. They were rumored to bring familial extermination on anyone who saw them, but were eventually killed by a man clearing the fields, enshrined, and banished to the mountains.

==References==
*[http://www2.kokugakuin.ac.jp/ijcc/wp/cpjr/kami/ito.html Evolution of the Concept of Kami]
*[http://www1.atwiki.jp/occultfantasy/pages/76.html 夜刀の神(ヤトノカミ・ヤツノカミ)] at [[ATWiki]].jp

{{Japan-myth-stub}}

[[Category:Japanese legendary creatures]]

[[ja:夜刀神]]
[[zh:夜刀神]]

